      <scopecontent id="aspace_60843be46425afa216389d7953a0bee3">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>This collection consists of photographic prints and digital images of Yale and New Haven buildings and locales, Yale football games, and other events.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
